# ── NeuroCoreLab: the ENGINE ships without any instance data ──
# When someone runs /ncl-init these get created and MUST stay private to their machine.
# The distributable repo tracks only *.template.md and the engine.

# Filled instance config (created from config/*.template.md)
config/*.md
!config/*.template.md

# Filled cortex (created from INDEX.template.md)
/INDEX.md

# The user's own neurons (their private knowledge)
decisiones/*.md
proyectos/**
propuestas/*.md
memoria/*.md
!**/.gitkeep

# Secrets & tokens — never here
secrets/
*.env
*.token

# Session log (regenerated) and tool noise
log/*.jsonl
.playwright-mcp/
*.pdf

# macOS
.DS_Store
